PeerIslands · Spec-Driven Development · 45-Minute Live Demo
============================================================

Pre-flight (5 minutes, run once before the demo)
------------------------------------------------

  1. Install uv:
     curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh

  2. Install spec-kit CLI (pinned to v0.7.0):
     uv tool install specify-cli --from git+https://github.com/github/spec-kit.git@v0.7.0

  3. Scaffold a fresh project wired for Claude Code:
     specify init smartinvoice --ai claude
     cd smartinvoice
     specify check

  4. Launch Claude Code inside the new project:
     claude

Then open peerislands-speckit-execution-guide.html in your browser
and start copy-pasting from Act 1 · Constitution.

Replay anytime
--------------

From this directory:
  ./reset-demo.sh              # wipes smartinvoice/, prints next steps
  ./reset-demo.sh --bootstrap  # wipes + re-runs specify init automatically

Prerequisites: Node 20 LTS, Git, and a MongoDB connection
(local mongodb://localhost:27017 or an Atlas M0 SRV URI).
